<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Sciophila georgei sp. nov., male terminalia A dorsal view B ventral view C lateral view D apical part of tergite IX, dorsal view E dorsal view, tergite IX removed F aedeagal complex, dorsal view G gonostylus, internal view H gonostylus, posterior view. Abbreviations: aed = aedeagus, cer = cercus, gc = gonocoxite, gc ap = gonocoxal apodeme, gst lbr = lateral branch of gonostylus, gst mbr = medial branch of gonostylus, gst sibr = small internal branch of gonostylus, par = paramere, tg 9 = tergite IX. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 3. Habitus photos of new species A Sciophila georgei sp. nov., paratype B Anatella metae sp. nov., paratype C Leia katae sp. nov., holotype, terminalia detached. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/524675" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/524674" .

